Main waha ja chuka hoon ...
Tu Jahan reh chuka hain (2)

Mere dil mein kahi tu chupa to nhi
Muskurata hua tu yahi hain kahi 
Dhundta fir raha ik nishani teri 
Mil bhi Jaye to puchhu kahani meri
Kis liye kis liye 
Ji raha hoon yahan ...

Milon hobe koto dine 
O amar moner manusher ero shone
